citation.title: Voyage Around the Erythraean Sea
citation.description: A collection of locations mentioned in the "Periplus of the Erythraean Sea" itinerary written in the early first century by an unknown author believed to be a merchant or scholar.
citation.source: The Voyage Around the Erythraean Sea. Accessed October 12, 2022. http://depts.washington.edu/silkroad/texts/periplus/periplus.html.
